author: The Telegraph
title: Competition: Win Rugby World Cup 2015 tickets with MasterCard
text: As a Worldwide Partner of Rugby World Cup 2015, MasterCard is offering Telegraph readers the chance to win tickets to the Rugby World Cup 2015 England v Wales match at Twickenham Stadium on Saturday, September 26, 2015. There are two pairs of tickets up for grabs so enter this prize draw now for the chance to win. To enter this fantastic prize draw, complete the form below before 9am on Thursday, 24 September 2015: Online Form - Win Rugby World Cup 2015 England v Wales tickets with MasterCard telegraph.co.uk Follow @telegraph
